name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: VU Quiz Firewall Bypass: Allow GDB & Quiz Copy/Paste - Skip Lesson Videos

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enable copy paste on quiz and gdb pages, mark lesson videos as viewed, and bypass VU quiz firewall.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Introducing the VU Quiz Firewall Bypass Chrome Extension, a powerful tool designed to enhance your virtual learning experience. With this innovative extension, you can effortlessly bypass restrictions to enable seamless copying and pasting during quizzes, saving you valuable time and effort. Additionally, say goodbye to tedious lesson videos with the ability to skip them at your discretion, allowing you to focus on the material that matters most to you. Whether you're a student looking to optimize your study routine or an educator seeking greater flexibility in your online teaching methods, this extension is the ultimate solution. Streamline your learning process and take control of your virtual classroom environment with the VU Quiz Firewall Bypass Chrome Extension.
